task.summary: Default task

Add new Svg files for grid and menu icons
This commit includes the addition of new SVG files for various grid and menu icons. These icons are related to the categories of grid, frames, and other UI elements. They all share a bold style, and are stored under the 'vuesax' library within 'dist/assets/icons'.

The version of the flowbite library referenced in the index.html file of the dist directory has been updated. This change was made to ensure we are using the latest stable version, providing the most recent bug fixes and features.

Update CSS styles for responsive design
The hard-coded height values in certain CSS classes were removed and changed to 'auto' to accommodate dynamic content lengths. This adjustment makes the design more responsive and fits better with different content sizes. The min-height property of the .cardEventLateralMovil class was also removed for a more flexible layout on mobile view.
